n\n===International===\n{{updated|match played 12 October 2018}}<ref name=NFT>{{NFT player |id=47777 |name=Grigg, Will |accessdate=6 September 2016}}</ref>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team||Year||Apps||Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=5|[[Northern Ireland national football team|Northern Ireland]]\n|2012||1||0\n|-\n|2013||4||0\n|-\n|2015||2||0\n|-\n|2016||3||1\n|-\n|2018||3||1\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total||13||2\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n:''As of match played 8 September 2018. Northern Ireland score listed first, score column indicates score after each Grigg goal.''<ref name=NFT/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|+ International goals by date, venue, cap, opponent, score, result and competition\n|-\n!scope=col|No.\n!scope=col data-sort-type=date|Date\n!scope=col|Venue\n!scope=col|Cap\n!scope=col|Opponent\n!scope=col|Score\n!scope=col|Result\n!scope=col|Competition\n!scope=col|{{abbr|Ref|Reference}}\n|-\n!scope=row|1\n|27 May 2016||[[Windsor Park]], [[Belfast]], Northern Ireland||align=center|8||{{fb|BLR}}||align=center|'''3'''\u20130||align=center|3\u20130||[[Exhibition game#Association football|Friendly]]||<ref>{{cite news |first=Lyle |last=Jackson |title=Northern Ireland 3\u20130 Belarus |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36339187 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=27 May 2016 |accessdate=6 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|2\n|8 September 2018||Windsor Park, Belfast, Northern Ireland||align=center|11||{{fb|BIH}}||align=center|'''1'''\u20132||align=center|1\u20132||[[2018\u201319 UEFA Nations League B]]||\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n===Club===\n'''Brentford'''\n*[[Football League One]] runner-up: [[2013\u201314 Football League One|2013\u201314]]<ref>{{cite book |editor-first=John |editor-last=Anderson |title=Sky Sports Football Yearbook 2014\u20132015 |year=2014 |publisher=Headline Publishing Group |location=London |isbn=978-1-4722-1251-1 |pages=74\u201375}}</ref>\n\n'''M