/10292763/will-grigg-wins-pfa-fans-league-one-player-of-the-season-award |title=Will Grigg wins PFA Fans' League One Player of the Season award |publisher=Sky Sports |date=25 May 2016 |accessdate=5 September 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Walsall F.C.|Walsall]] Player of the Season: [[2012\u201313 Walsall F.C. season|2012\u201313]]<ref name=skysports />\n*Walsall Players' Player of the Season: [[2012\u201313 Walsall F.C. season|2012\u201313]]<ref name=skysports />\n*[[Football League One Player of the Month]]: April 2016,<ref>{{cite web |title=Will Grigg named Sky Bet League 1 Player of the Month |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/news/article/2016/will-grigg-named-sky-bet-league-1-player-of-the-month-3096365.aspx |publisher=The Football League |accessdate=10 October 2017}}</ref> April 2018<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.efl.com/news/2018/may/player-of-the-month-will-grigg-wigan-athletic/ |title=Player of the Month: Will Grigg \u2013 Wigan Athletic |publisher=EFL |date=4 May 2018 |accessdate=5 September 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20160505180015/http://www.wiganlatics.co.uk/team/player-profile/will-grigg/9 Will Grigg profile] at the official [[Wigan Athletic F.C.]] website\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20160508234359/http://www.irishfa.com/ifa-international/squads/senior-men/will-grigg Will Grigg profile] at the official [[Irish Football Association]] website\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Awards\n| bg = gold\n| fg = navy\n| list1 = \n{{2015\u201316 Football League One PFA Team of the Year}}\n{{2017\u201318 EFL League One PFA Team of the Year}}\n{{Football League One top scorers}}\n{{Walsall F.C. Player of the Season}}\n}}\n{{Northern Ireland squad UEFA Euro 2016}}\n{{Sunderland A.F.C. squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Grigg, Will}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Solihull]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:Association footballers from North